---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Ishan"
  description="Frontend Engineer, minimalist, and builder of things."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="about-main">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        <span class="back-arrow">←</span> all posts
      </a>

      <header class="about-header">
        <p class="label">// who-is-ishan</p>
        <h1 class="about-title display-serif">Hey, I'm Ishan. ✌️</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-body">
        <p>
          I’m a <strong>Frontend Engineer</strong> currently working at QuestionPro. I build 
          interfaces for BI tools that try to make sense of massive datasets. My daily 
          bread is React and Next.js, but I’ve been spending a lot of my time lately 
          learning about <strong>Apache Kafka</strong> and how to handle data at scale.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm based in Pune, living in a minimalist space that helps me keep my 
          focus sharp. My routine is pretty simple: <strong>one cup of coffee and 
          exactly three teas</strong>. When I need to clear my head, I’m usually 
          out on my <strong>bike</strong> or catching up on <em>One-Punch Man</em>.
        </p>

        <p>
          This site is essentially my public notebook. I use it to document the 
          problems I run into, the patterns I’m learning, and the occasional 
          deep dive into systems that catch my interest. No noise, just the signal.
        </p>

        <h2>The Toolkit</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> React, Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind</li>
          <li><strong>Data & Systems:</strong> Apache Kafka, Node.js</li>
          <li><strong>Focus:</strong> Frontend architecture, system design and scalable web systems</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Beyond the code</h2>
        <p>
          When I’m not at my desk, I’m usually keeping an eye on my investments, 
          planning the next trip to Goa, or thinking about finally starting 
          that workout routine. I’m a fan of clean abstractions, simple 
          living, and high-quality tea.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          If you want to talk about frontend architecture, distributed systems, 
          or why Naruto is still elite, hit me up.
        </p>
        <p>
          Find me on <a href="https://github.com/ishanbagchi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> 
          or drop a line via <a href="mailto:hi@ishanbagchi.com">email</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-main {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: var(--space-16);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  /* ─── Back link ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-gold); }

  .back-arrow { transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .back-link:hover .back-arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

  /* ─── Page header ────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  /* ─── Body ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-body {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .about-body strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-body em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-body li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .about-body li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .about-body a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gold-dim);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .about-body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>